{"tid":2331643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瑞典收緊防疫措施　首次建議民眾公共交通上戴口罩","createTime":"2020-12-19T03:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T06:05:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bca40f5f30aa4c68ac1d867ff2aaf9545a80da32","tid":2331643,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:20:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566165-20201219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566165-20201219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBer6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=d5073ca2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566165-20201219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6c182a36\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566165-20201219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞典政府收緊防疫措施，首次建議民眾在公共交通工具上戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n首相勒文表示，希望民眾意識到目前疫情的嚴重性，如果新措施無法有效執行，政府將關閉更多公共場所。<br />\n<br />\n一直沒有封城的瑞典，將於24日起收緊防疫措施，包括餐廳每枱人數限制在4人、餐廳晚上8時後禁止賣酒、商場限制人流並取消聖誕和新年的減價促銷活動等。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典累計36萬7千多人確診，超過8千人不治，兩個數字均居北歐五國之首。瑞典公共衛生局一直以「未有科學研究依據」為由不建議民眾戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n另外，繼荷蘭和德國後，意大利和奧地利亦會「封城」，防止疫情在聖誕和新年期間惡化。"},{"pid":"d21d4ba2244df770bedce87703085d76d0879e82","tid":2331643,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:20:50.000Z","msg":"青山熱狗唔衝去瑞典話人恐懼撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10bea892379c2b18e110760aefd276742876fa3","tid":2331643,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d21d4ba2244df770bedce87703085d76d0879e82","tid":2331643,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:20:50.000Z","msg":"青山熱狗唔衝去瑞典話人恐懼撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"佢哋好快會po瑞典嘅死亡數字<br />\n話其實好少<br />\n但係唔會同瑞典鄰國挪威同芬蘭比較<br />\n挪威芬蘭上個月死亡各100<br />\n但係瑞典就死1700"},{"pid":"20e5a600498fa46425b2777ee562d97f9a450524","tid":2331643,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}